{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"ccbf11e9-1556-4ac4-961d-2a9b2bf0acbf","content":"The project directory doesn't exist yet, but here's what you need to configure in your `.csproj` to publish as a dotnet tool to NuGet.org:\n\n```xml\n<Project Sdk=\"Microsoft.NET.Sdk\">\n  <PropertyGroup>\n    <OutputType>Exe</OutputType>\n    <TargetFramework>net8.0</TargetFramework>\n\n    <!-- Required for dotnet tool -->\n    <PackAsTool>true</PackAsTool>\n    <ToolCommandName>my-mcp-server</ToolCommandName>\n\n    <!-- NuGet package metadata -->\n    <PackageId>MyMcpServer</PackageId>\n    <Version>1.0.0</Version>\n    <Authors>YourName</Authors>\n    <Description>An MCP server for ...</Description>\n    <PackageReadmeFile>README.md</PackageReadmeFile>\n    <PackageLicenseExpression>MIT</PackageLicenseExpression>\n    <RepositoryUrl>https://github.com/you/repo</RepositoryUrl>\n  </PropertyGroup>\n\n  <!-- Include README in package -->\n  <ItemGroup>\n    <None Include=\"README.md\" Pack=\"true\" PackagePath=\"/\" />\n  </ItemGroup>\n</Project>\n```\n\n**Key properties:**\n\n| Property | Purpose |\n|---|---|\n| `PackAsTool` | Marks the project as a dotnet tool |\n| `ToolCommandName` | The CLI command users will run |\n| `PackageId` | Unique ID on NuGet.org |\n\n**Publishing steps:**\n\n```bash\n# Pack\ndotnet pack -c Release\n\n# Push (get API key from nuget.org/account/apikeys)\ndotnet nuget push bin/Release/MyMcpServer.1.0.0.nupkg \\\n  --api-key YOUR_API_KEY \\\n  --source https://api.nuget.org/v3/index.json\n```\n\n**Users install with:**\n\n```bash\ndotnet tool install -g MyMcpServer\nmy-mcp-server   # runs your stdio MCP server\n```\n\nSince your server uses stdio transport, no additional configuration is needed — `PackAsTool` preserves the console app behavior that stdio requires.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"ff6d4bb7-815b-4e32-b834-1792a1d4b802","outputTokens":548,"requestId":"7FD3:3ADEAF:47E28FA:4E75DD1:69F15C00"},"id":"3e28dc3f-1fd4-4d66-aab1-a1dd488aeb94","timestamp":"2026-04-29T01:16:57.871Z","parentId":"1ee41996-1c31-4406-a379-846ffdf04c6a"}
